<br />\n唔知係咪大膽啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實幾sad下,諗下點解外國既動物唔會驚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係香港都成日有貓摸的,差在有無留意姐<br />\n<br />\n反而香港d鳥類就全部驚人.."},{"pid":"f1ebe4b93ecd5656a2223ff54fc9091ec8c88e79","tid":380193,"uid":39138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>證明你受貓貓歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係香港無咩貓貓搵我玩<br />\n係歐洲真係見親都捉住我<br />\n唔知係咪大膽啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實幾sad下,諗下點解外國既動物唔會驚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得外國啲貓可以放養由佢地自己行黎行去好正<br />\n感覺佢地開心啲</blockquote><br />\n外國真係多數放養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  地方大 又唔驚會跳樓</blockquote><br />\n我外國fd放養佢隻貓<br />\n然後佢話佢隻貓跟左其他貓做大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00d994ad7ab8735c1e438f6e7fb4135dc7239af","tid":380193,"uid":39138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:27:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n係香港都成日有貓摸的,差在有無留意姐<br />\n<br />\n反而香港d鳥類就全部驚人..</blockquote><br />\n香港啲貓警戒心好重咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e38568562117fb5e5358eacbd43ad082800bdc9","tid":380193,"uid":56280,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n係香港都成日有貓摸的,差在有無留意姐<br />\n<br />\n反而香港d鳥類就全部驚人..</blockquote><br />\n香港啲貓警戒心好重咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊<br />\n<br />\n我屋企果隻八婆都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iehvgrwk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiehvgrwk&h=ca1b4ca8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"948e73d72fade363eaf58d1c238e2285c5aa7cf6","tid":380193,"uid":40460,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n係香港都成日有貓摸的,差在有無留意姐<br />\n<br />\n反而香港d鳥類就全部驚人..</blockquote><br />\n香港啲貓警戒心好重咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得同人、同啲家長有關<br />\n我屋企樓下都有好多貓<br />\n雖然啲呀嬸同後生女會好錫佢哋<br />\n但係見過啲細路拎波掟貓，佢老母都唔柒理<br />\n又有啲用拐杖嘅呀伯打貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有變態佬虐殺啲貓<br />\n<br />\n你做貓見到你啲朋友比啲閪人咁對待都會有戒心"},{"pid":"993e30e99560030235ae322c917e2494948559ff","tid":380193,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:43:22.000Z","msg":"弓形蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa45f1ea6912faa9269f8f1514d30f3e7ba0ec2","tid":380193,"uid":39138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我覺得同人、同啲家長有關<br />\n我屋企樓下都有好多貓<br />\n雖然啲呀嬸同後生女會好錫佢哋<br />\n但係見過啲細路拎波掟貓，佢老母都唔柒理<br />\n又有啲用拐杖嘅呀伯打貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有變態佬虐殺啲貓<br />\n<br />\n你做貓見到你啲朋友比啲閪人咁對待都會有戒心</blockquote><br />\n我屋企樓下都有好多街貓<br />\n我聽過最仆街係啲人call漁農<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好慘"},{"pid":"a13123e1cfe372aa4fb855dcc0d764c4565410ab","tid":380193,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"好想奶"},{"pid":"1082ec7196fd350e202844fbbd0db5a99274c46f","tid":380193,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:00:53.000Z","msg":"弓形蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a6646951e43c8d2cca121e5bc6baa92424ab59","tid":380193,"uid":47055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9ded87821165593c37a9aabdb8d30751a00750","tid":380193,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"