>\n但係隻貓驚男人<br />\n又當左我個friend係男人（短頭髮）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死都唔夠膽行埋我個friend度<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/192341_ad81f2f2bb4de4868ecac0662636e191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F192341_ad81f2f2bb4de4868ecac0662636e191.jpg&h=3fdb0473&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪咸濕貓黎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ee014273e64665ba9e71f61907812116696b61","tid":380193,"uid":125382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我發覺歐洲好多貓都好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲毛硬到好似針咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61d34b1f947c7ccab51b78f56dba7c5242d8e1d","tid":380193,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明你受貓貓歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貓公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722697169179210bdbe60d04d06fc31092f3216b","tid":380193,"uid":40460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前係英國Camden market 都有隻街貓嗲人<br />\n啲毛勁滑<br />\n我同個friend (女）一齊去撚貓<br />\n但係隻貓驚男人<br />\n又當左我個friend係男人（短頭髮）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死都唔夠膽行埋我個friend度<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/192341_ad81f2f2bb4de4868ecac0662636e191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F192341